Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.13,0:00:14.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The hee-row?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.58,0:00:17.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes, he protects the human world.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.25,0:00:20.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The hero is powerful beyond words...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.96,0:00:24.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Just to speak of him sends chills down my spine!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.25,0:00:29.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,He defeated Chaos Lord Belial,\Nthe mighty Sorcerer Lord Astarot,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.29,0:00:33.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,and countless other brave warriors of eld!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.29,0:00:41.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Young lady, should you become our Queen,\Ndo not engage the hero in combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.04,0:00:45.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Fighting him would lead to your destruction!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.50,0:00:49.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, please! That's so dumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.13,0:00:54.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I don't know why you're so afraid of this heerow.\NHe's just a human!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.08,0:00:58.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If I ever saw him, I'd give him a beat-down!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.33,0:01:02.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Not like I'm ever gonna choose to be Queen, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.75,0:01:12.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You told me you want to save\Nthe Demon World, right, Echidna?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.08,0:01:16.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You said you'd endure blood, sweat, and tears...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.21,0:01:21.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,to obtain the stone and bring peace to fruition.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.00,0:01:25.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Blood, sweat, and tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.67,0:01:28.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The time to prove your mettle is now!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.04,0:01:40.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If you want the Stone, if you want to save the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.04,0:01:42.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,then stop me, here and now,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.13,0:01:44.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,brave heroes!
