Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.46,0:03:33.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Leo, you fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.13,0:03:46.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.38,0:03:56.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Are you mad?! Have you lost your mind?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.00,0:04:01.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Queen Echidna!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.08,0:04:05.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Nope, my mind's all here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.92,0:04:08.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,My job is to keep this world safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.00,0:04:10.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's the reason I was made.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.04,0:04:13.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The only reason I live for!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.00,0:04:20.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A single swing is that powerful?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.17,0:04:28.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If I can't save the world, I'll lose my whole identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.25,0:04:35.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If humanity doesn't need me,\Nthen I'll make them need me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.04,0:04:39.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll save the world, even if I have to destroy it first!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.71,0:04:43.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You would decide to switch ends and means!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.96,0:04:47.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Why would you destroy\Nthe very thing you want to protect?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.63,0:04:50.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,All that would await you is a devastated land!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.71,0:04:53.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Devastation! Hell, I'll take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.17,0:04:57.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I've protected this world long enough.\NWho cares if I destroy it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.46,0:05:03.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Leo...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.38,0:05:09.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Emptying everything out and starting\Nfrom scratch sounds pretty damn good!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.71,0:05:28.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Lord Leo, enough of this foolishness!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.46,0:05:31.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Calm yourself! This isn't like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.42,0:05:34.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,He's right! Why do we have to fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.54,0:05:38.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Have you been paying attention, you moron Generals?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.33,0:05:42.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Obsidian Cage!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.96,0:06:03.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A binding spell? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.67,0:06:07.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If you want my heart, then you're going to have to kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.92,0:06:10.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.96,0:06:13.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If your heart really is the Philosopher's Stone,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.08,0:06:17.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,then why not continue to help us,\Nas you've been doing this whole time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.25,0:06:21.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You said you wouldn't betray us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.46,0:06:26.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Or was that all a lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.00,0:06:29.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Were we never friends at all?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.83,0:06:35.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If you don't kill me, then you'll all die.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.21,0:06:41.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Edvard!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.13,0:06:49.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Edvard...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.83,0:06:53.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Leo, you really mean to kill us...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.71,0:06:58.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm sick of it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.13,0:06:59.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,My hyper-reactive skill improvement,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.58,0:07:02.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,my existence as an immortal guardian\Nfor humanity, all of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.29,0:07:04.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm not even allowed to die to end it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.04,0:07:07.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I just keep protecting, guarding, defending,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.08,0:07:14.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,and even when they finally say\Nthey don't need me, it doesn't end!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.38,0:07:19.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Leo, you bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.13,0:07:22.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Who should I hate, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.08,0:07:24.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The humans who made me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.79,0:07:28.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Or the demons who forced their hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.04,0:07:37.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.88,0:07:41.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,All of you, that's who.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.38,0:07:45.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So I'll destroy both the human AND the demon worlds...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.54,0:07:49.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,and quit all this heroing bullshit once and for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.21,0:08:22.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No... I knew he was holding back when we fought before,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.50,0:08:26.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,but is this his true strength?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.13,0:08:32.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What now? I can't fight him in this state...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.63,0:08:38.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And my mana core hasn't yet fully\Nrecovered from our last battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.21,0:08:42.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Is this the time to use that spell?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.46,0:08:46.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It would still be a gamble.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.92,0:08:49.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And I have no idea if it will work...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.38,0:08:52.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Please stop, Leo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.33,0:08:53.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Lily?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.25,0:08:55.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Please, don't do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.71,0:09:00.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,This isn't like you, Leo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.75,0:09:08.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Do you remember when we were on Largo,\Nand you listened when I had problems?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.88,0:09:11.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You told me tons of really good advice, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.63,0:09:15.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yep, I did. I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.29,0:09:19.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's my turn to return the favor!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.04,0:09:22.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So tell me all your problems! I'll hear you out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.13,0:09:29.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So please, stop! Let's not fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.88,0:09:32.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.58,0:09:34.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Leo...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.75,0:09:40.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,My problems? ALL my problems?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.21,0:09:45.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You want to hear what my problems are, Lily?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.33,0:09:48.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I do! I'll hear you out, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.75,0:09:51.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Right now, my biggest problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.79,0:09:52.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.38,0:09:54.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,My biggest problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.79,0:10:02.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,...is that the heroes I expected so much\Nfrom are so goddamn weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.79,0:10:11.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Lily!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.04,0:10:20.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I get it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.83,0:10:25.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're no hero... Not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.46,0:10:33.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No real hero would ruthlessly attack\Na harmless, unarmed opponent!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.96,0:10:45.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Fill my hands with the piercing rays of the gods!\NDestroy mine enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.21,0:10:48.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Gae Assail!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.54,0:11:02.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So you finally got serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.63,0:11:07.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Not even high-level spells can hurt him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.42,0:11:09.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Come, heroes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.21,0:11:16.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If you want your world to survive,\Nthen stop me with every last fiber of your being!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.42,0:11:19.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Very well!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.50,0:11:24.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I am grateful to you, Lord Leo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.04,0:11:32.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You taught this ignorant oaf to understand\Nthe weaknesses in those around him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.21,0:11:35.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You were a fine teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.04,0:11:38.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Never have I known a man such as you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.42,0:11:43.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You had my utmost respect, from the bottom of my heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.21,0:11:47.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You were a true ally and a friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.46,0:11:50.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And now you realize you were wrong?\NThat I was a villain?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.58,0:11:55.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No, I still feel that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.42,0:12:01.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But even if you are my friend...\NNo, BECAUSE you are my friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.63,0:12:04.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,He's unleashed his dragon blood?!\NHe's getting serious, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.75,0:12:08.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If you have strayed from the path,\Nit is my duty to cut you down!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.46,0:12:15.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.25,0:12:16.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Cocytus Ptolomea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.33,0:12:19.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.42,0:12:21.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Inferno Gehenna.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.00,0:12:24.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,He's casting spells with opposing elements\Nat the same time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.04,0:12:30.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Edvard!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.54,0:12:33.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And now your precious dragon scales are all but useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.63,0:12:35.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Destroyed by a rapid change in temperature.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.88,0:12:38.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Know how that works? Probably not, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.50,0:12:45.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Begone, Dragon General.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.92,0:12:51.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Two down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.04,0:12:53.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,This villain...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.29,0:13:04.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Leo...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.08,0:13:09.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Do not discount the Demon Queen's strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.33,0:13:11.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Behemoth Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.92,0:13:12.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Earthen Grave!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.25,0:13:16.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Good work! Now burn to your death!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.92,0:13:17.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Inferno!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.04,0:13:39.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.79,0:13:41.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.04,0:13:47.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,After being hit with that many attacks,\Nhe's suffered almost no damage?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.38,0:13:55.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wait... His special ability is\N'hyper-reactive skill improvement', right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.17,0:14:00.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,He copies the abilities of others and\Nendlessly improves upon them...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.88,0:14:03.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Does that apply to defense, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.38,0:14:08.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If he grows stronger with every foe he faces,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.58,0:14:11.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,with every attack that hits him...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.75,0:14:15.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No. This doesn't fare well for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.42,0:14:16.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If this battle continues...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.00,0:14:30.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I thought you'd be next, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.79,0:14:34.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I must be out of practice. Thought that was a sure kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.71,0:14:38.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That was a perfect strike. He's just a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.17,0:14:41.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Good point. And a real pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.08,0:14:43.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Keep at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.79,0:14:53.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So what is it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.75,0:14:56.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Do you wanna die, or do you wanna be killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.75,0:14:58.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Both!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.92,0:15:04.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I want to fight the world and get killed by someone,\Nanyone, out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.92,0:15:07.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, I'm gonna destroy the whole world myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.08,0:15:08.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.21,0:15:14.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You didn't need to join the army to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.33,0:15:16.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You could've just started your endless fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.04,0:15:20.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Instead, you came over here and\Ngot all passionate about helping people,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.75,0:15:22.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,teaching them how to work more efficiently and crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.67,0:15:27.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You were thinking ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.63,0:15:30.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Thinking about the people who would survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.75,0:15:34.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't care about that\Nif you really wanted to destroy the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.83,0:15:38.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Shut up, Mernes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.88,0:15:46.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You don't hate the world.\NYou don't want to kill the humans, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.92,0:15:50.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I know what you're really after!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.33,0:15:57.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Mernes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.67,0:16:03.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A below-freezing auto-counter?! How powerful is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.67,0:16:05.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That makes three.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.04,0:16:11.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What I'm really after, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.21,0:16:12.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I told you what I'm really after!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.79,0:16:17.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I want to save the world, even if I have to destroy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.79,0:16:24.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're finally ready to fight me, huh, Lily?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.96,0:16:27.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna fight. I don't wanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.38,0:16:31.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna have to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.00,0:16:34.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But Leo...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.42,0:16:38.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You don't look like you're having any fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.13,0:16:42.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're smiling, but you're not happy at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.29,0:16:46.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So I'll help... I'll stop you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.63,0:16:52.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Because I love you, Leo... I love you a whole lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.92,0:16:56.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So I'll help you by stopping you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.42,0:16:58.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Lily...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.63,0:17:05.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Fine, then. Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.54,0:17:22.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Right then, I realized the truth once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.33,0:17:25.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Leo was neither human nor demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.38,0:17:31.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,He was a monster, created by ancient humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.71,0:17:34.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We can't win like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.63,0:17:38.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,He'll kill us, then humanity,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.71,0:17:41.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,then the Demon World, then the future...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.75,0:17:45.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I've no time left to falter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.04,0:17:52.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Shutina, I'm using it. Buy me 42 seconds of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.29,0:17:58.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Honestly, my Queen? 42 seconds against Leo?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.96,0:18:03.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I have no one else to turn to. If you cannot,\Nthat's the end of everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.88,0:18:08.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'll do it, of course. Why wouldn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.83,0:18:12.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's just one more impossible demand\Nyou've foisted upon me, like every other!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.25,0:18:17.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. If we make it back alive,\NI'll treat you to the finest wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.00,0:18:22.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,This may be my one and only chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.13,0:18:28.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But if I'm correct about Leo's true objective,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.33,0:18:32.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,then I might be able to win. I might be able to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.75,0:18:35.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A spell?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.83,0:18:41.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes. Now that I am abdicating\Nmy throne to you, I must pass it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.92,0:18:44.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What, just because I'm your daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.83,0:18:47.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Please, that doesn't mean--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.08,0:18:49.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No, never mind. Forget I said anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.88,0:18:53.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Cease your prattling, former Demon King Cychreus.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.71,0:18:56.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I need not your assistance, nor any secret royal magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.79,0:18:59.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I don't want to have to pass it down,\Neither, but I don't have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.42,0:19:03.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,This spell has been passed down from\NDemon King to Demon King for centuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.75,0:19:04.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Centuries?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.58,0:19:06.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You know of the Hero, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.46,0:19:12.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Of course. The Hero that defeated\Nso many of our brethren long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.00,0:19:16.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Astarot devised a spell to assist in battle against him,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.54,0:19:19.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,one designed solely for defeating the Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.21,0:19:21.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Solely for defeating him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.58,0:19:26.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The spell is highly limited in its uses\Nand is extremly costly to cast.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.00,0:19:29.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I know not of any Demon King who has yet to use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.79,0:19:33.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,To be completely honest, the spell itself\Nis no more than a gamble.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.21,0:19:36.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Then I may never use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.38,0:19:43.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I needn't rely on such a gamble, nor fear him.\NThe full extent of my power will be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.92,0:19:49.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I thought you'd say that. Maybe you'll be all right, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.63,0:19:50.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Of course I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.96,0:19:56.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Neph salem arcranus elgil hel...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.08,0:19:56.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Leo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.42,0:20:03.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I've known for too long that you are a terrible liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.38,0:20:07.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You could've killed Edvard,\Nbut you just sent him flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.00,0:20:10.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You interrupted Mernes before\Nhe could finish his sentence!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.92,0:20:13.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You even hesitated when Lily offered to help!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.29,0:20:17.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You don't want to destroy the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.17,0:20:22.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The only thing you hate,\Nthe only thing you want to destroy,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.50,0:20:23.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,is yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.50,0:20:28.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're afraid of your future.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.21,0:20:33.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A future where you want to save the world,\Nbut can't, where your life has no meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.38,0:20:38.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're afraid that you might actually destroy\Nthe world in an attempt to save it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.58,0:20:39.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm right, aren't I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.13,0:20:54.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So you've forced yourself to play the villain,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.96,0:20:58.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,all in a bid to get us to defeat you\Nwhile you're still sane and in control.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.38,0:21:02.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,After ensuring your Philosopher's Stone\Nand your work is passed on
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.54,0:21:06.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,and knowing that humans and demons\Nwill ally with one another when you're gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.42,0:21:09.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.92,0:21:14.67,Subtitle-2,,0,0,0,,Six chains, twelve swords to avenge the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.50,0:21:14.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm almost there! Don't die on me, Shutina!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.08,0:21:16.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Don't you dare die!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.04,0:21:19.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Is that the best you could do\Nafter three thousand years of life?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.00,0:21:23.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Leo,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.67,0:21:26.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.13,0:21:35.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Enough already. Die.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.17,0:21:41.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's YOU who will die here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.79,0:21:43.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Listen well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.63,0:21:50.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,This spell will use all of your mana to disable\Nthe Hero's abilities for a brief moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.96,0:21:52.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We call it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.08,0:21:53.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hero binding spell:
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.17,0:21:55.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Anti-Leo!
